    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "oh okay that makes sense. so if i'm trying to get a really good crust on a loaf of sourdough, what exactly is going on at a molecular level during that process? like why does it change the flavor so much instead of just making it look dark?",
      "source": "evaluator"
    },
